    <url>/2023/10/09/apollo-0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="apollo-env-setup"><a href="#apollo-env-setup" class="headerlink" title="apollo env setup"></a>apollo env setup</h1><p><a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/community/article/1030">link1</a><br><a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/community/article/1031">link2</a><br><a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/community/cloud-lab">学习资料</a></p><h2 id="场景的同步"><a href="#场景的同步" class="headerlink" title="场景的同步"></a>场景的同步</h2><p>可以进入<a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/workspace">工作台</a>创建场景集，然后通过<a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/community/article/104">同步场景</a>生成同步的命令，在容器运行即可同步。<br>另外也可以在场景添加&#x2F;编辑自己的<a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/workspace/scenario-management">场景集</a></p><h2 id="xh-lab"><a href="#xh-lab" class="headerlink" title="xh-lab"></a>xh-lab</h2><p><a href="https://apollo.baidu.com/community/course/outline/2?activeId=248">教程</a></p><h3 id="0x01-CyberRT-listener-and-talker"><a href="#0x01-CyberRT-listener-and-talker" class="headerlink" title="0x01 CyberRT listener and talker"></a>0x01 CyberRT listener and talker</h3>]]></content>
    
    
    
